# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:16
translate spanish jez3_b7d0283a:

    # "Detective Rodriguez picks up the phone after a single ring, as if she had been holding her phone in her hand."
    "La detective Rodríguez descuelga al primer tono, como si tuviera el teléfono en la mano."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:18
translate spanish jez3_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/jez_answering.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_answering.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:19
translate spanish jez3_6673062e:

    # det "Detective Rodriguez."
    det "Detective Rodríguez."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:20
translate spanish jez3_416b4b28:

    # pc "Hello, this is [pcname]."
    pc "Hola, soy [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:22
translate spanish jez3_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/jez_hey.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_hey.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:23
translate spanish jez3_5f1522eb:

    # det "Hey, [pcname]. What's up?"
    det "Hola, [pcname]. ¿Qué tal?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:24
translate spanish jez3_eb667b3e:

    # pc "I had some new information about my dad's case. I was able to get into his laptop."
    pc "Tengo información nueva sobre el caso de mi padre. He conseguido acceder a su portátil."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:25
translate spanish jez3_a1187622:

    # pc "I found a bunch of e-mails between him and this Whitney person."
    pc "He encontrado un montón de correos electrónicos entre él y una tal Whitney."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:26
translate spanish jez3_d2f98bdb:

    # det "Hey, [pcname]. Hold on a second."
    det "Hola, [pcname]. Espera un momento."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:28
translate spanish jez3_77774b9f:

    # det "I'll be honest with you. I've had a really bad day and I have a migraine from hell."
    det "Voy a ser sincera contigo. He tenido un día horrible y tengo una migraña de infarto."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:29
translate spanish jez3_b0a1faa8:

    # det "Your voice on this phone is making my head pound. What do you say we meet up in person."
    det "Tu voz por teléfono me está haciendo doler la cabeza. ¿Qué te parece si nos vemos en persona?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:30
translate spanish jez3_7cfb0b0e:

    # det "Do you know where The Pit is?"
    det "¿Sabes dónde está The Pit?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:31
translate spanish jez3_5a003c29:

    # pc "The bar downtown?"
    pc "¿El bar del centro?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:32
translate spanish jez3_c60f38c7:

    # det "That's it. Want to meet me there and have this conversation over drinks?"
    det "Exacto. ¿Quieres que quedemos allí y tengamos esta conversación tomando algo?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:33
translate spanish jez3_a5c9c049:

    # det "I could really use a drink."
    det "Me vendría muy bien un trago."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:36
translate spanish jez3_2ba5f0eb:

    # det "Great, I'll be there in two."
    det "Genial, estaré allí en dos minutos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:38
translate spanish jez3_cd4d07e3:

    # det "Come on man, give me a break."
    det "Venga ya, tómate un respiro."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:39
translate spanish jez3_84d27d16:

    # det "I just got finished working a 24-hour shift."
    det "Acabo de terminar un turno de 24 horas."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:40
translate spanish jez3_cd598c64:

    # pc "Alright, I'll be there in five minutes."
    pc "Vale, estaré allí en cinco minutos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:41
translate spanish jez3_2ba5f0eb_1:

    # det "Great, I'll be there in two."
    det "Genial, estaré allí en dos minutos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:44
translate spanish jez3_d1ed5b1b:

    # "She hangs up and I quickly get ready and head out to the car."
    "Cuelga y yo me preparo rápidamente y salgo hacia el coche."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:45
translate spanish jez3_5ddb21e5:

    # "Only a few minutes later, I park in front of the bar."
    "Solo unos minutos después, aparco delante del bar."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:47
translate spanish jez3_23e3b6db:

    # "I walk in and am met with a cloud of cigarette smoke, the dull roar of conversation, and a jukebox playing some rock song I've never heard."
    "Entro y me recibe una nube de humo de cigarrillo, el murmullo sordo de las conversaciones y una gramola que pone una canción de rock que nunca he oído."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:48
translate spanish jez3_64d6327f:

    # "It takes a few moments for me to notice Detective Rodriguez waving at me from a booth in the back of the bar."
    "Tardo unos segundos en darme cuenta de que la detective Rodríguez me está haciendo señas desde una mesa al fondo del bar."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:49
translate spanish jez3_398f4ad8:

    # "I walk over and sit down across from her."
    "Me acerco y me siento frente a ella."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:53
translate spanish jez3_71bded69:

    # det "Thanks for meeting me here. I know it's not very professional, but I need a drink real bad and I hate drinking alone."
    det "Gracias por quedar aquí conmigo. Sé que no es muy profesional, pero me apetece mucho tomarme una copa y odio beber sola."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:54
translate spanish jez3_ac23b499:

    # det "I ordered you a beer too. You're twenty-one, right?"
    det "Te he pedido una cerveza también. Tienes veintiún años, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:55
translate spanish jez3_c2113814:

    # pc "Twenty-two."
    pc "Veintidós."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:56
translate spanish jez3_da9af380:

    # det "Good. Drink up then."
    det "Bien. Pues bébetela."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:59
translate spanish jez3_899cb188:

    # "I take a drink of the beer in front of me. It's nice and smooth."
    "Doy un sorbo a la cerveza que tengo delante. Está buena y suave."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:62
translate spanish jez3_cfdfe09b:

    # pc "I'm just here to talk."
    pc "Solo he venido a hablar."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:64
translate spanish jez3_a023156a:

    # det "So I'm just going to be drinking alone anyway. So be it."
    det "Así que voy a acabar bebiendo sola de todos modos. Que así sea."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:68
translate spanish jez3_e5c2530c:

    # det "Okay, so you got into your dad's laptop and found some correspondence?"
    det "Vale, ¿entraste en el portátil de tu padre y encontraste algo de correspondencia?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:69
translate spanish jez3_66708b9a:

    # pc "Yeah, and it's crazy."
    pc "Sí, y es una locura."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:70
translate spanish jez3_08461fea:

    # det "Give me the summary. You can send the entire thing over to my e-mail later."
    det "Resúmemelo. Ya me puedes enviar todo por correo electrónico más tarde."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:71
translate spanish jez3_2af7a240:

    # pc "Well the gist is that he and Whitney were planning a trip."
    pc "Bueno, la idea general es que él y Whitney estaban planeando un viaje."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:72
translate spanish jez3_b2a62e0b:

    # det "So he did run off with her?"
    det "¿Así que se fugó con ella?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:73
translate spanish jez3_d0c263e4:

    # pc "No, he was the only one going on this trip."
    pc "No, él era el único que iba a ir a ese viaje."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:74
translate spanish jez3_2908401f:

    # det "Okay, so where did he go?"
    det "Vale, ¿y adónde fue?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:75
translate spanish jez3_0a1d6430:

    # pc "I'm not sure, but the strangest part is how he got there."
    pc "No estoy segura, pero lo más extraño es cómo llegó allí."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:76
translate spanish jez3_09d6eafc:

    # det "Explain."
    det "Explícame."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:77
translate spanish jez3_61000743:

    # pc "He built some sort of device. I found it in the basement. It looks like a hula hoop."
    pc "Construyó una especie de artilugio. Lo encontré en el sótano. Parece un hula-hoop."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:79
translate spanish jez3_b0e7f9ea:

    # det "What? You lost me."
    det "¿Qué? No te sigo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:80
translate spanish jez3_40d85287:

    # pc "I don't know how to explain it. It looks like a hoop. He and Whitney built it together. When it's activated, it's supposed to transport you somewhere."
    pc "No sé cómo explicarlo. Parece un aro. Lo construyeron juntos, él y Whitney. Cuando se activa, se supone que te transporta a algún sitio."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:81
translate spanish jez3_1f06310c:

    # pc "He needed the diamonds to activate it. That's why he stole them."
    pc "Necesitaba los diamantes para activarlo. Por eso los robó."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:82
translate spanish jez3_35f3019c:

    # det "And the meth too?"
    det "¿Y la metanfetamina también?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:83
translate spanish jez3_ff210007:

    # pc "Right. He used the meth to speed his heart rate up so his heart didn't stop during the transportation."
    pc "Exacto. Usó la metanfetamina para acelerar su ritmo cardíaco y que su corazón no se detuviera durante el transporte."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:84
translate spanish jez3_22ea6d6f:

    # det "You know this is the dumbest fucking thing I've ever heard right?"
    det "Sabes que esto es la mayor tontería que he oído en mi vida, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:85
translate spanish jez3_a2fed6c2:

    # pc "I'm just telling you what they were talking about."
    pc "Solo te estoy contando de lo que hablaban."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:87
translate spanish jez3_1b198a7a:

    # det "Well I did look into the diamond theft."
    det "Bueno, investigué el robo de los diamantes."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:88
translate spanish jez3_0768d1c5:

    # det "There was a jewelry store over in Whiterock that was broken into only a few days before your dad went missing."
    det "Hubo un robo en una joyería de Whiterock solo unos días antes de que tu padre desapareciera."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:89
translate spanish jez3_727a0b8a:

    # det "It was just like you described. The security was disabled for only a minute."
    det "Fue tal y como lo describiste. La seguridad estuvo desactivada solo un minuto."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:90
translate spanish jez3_75b55784:

    # det "The thief entered through the back door, walked in, took two three-carat diamond rings, then walked back out."
    det "El ladrón entró por la puerta trasera, se metió dentro, cogió dos anillos de diamantes de tres quilates y luego salió."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:91
translate spanish jez3_a0cd13f9:

    # det "Security kicked back on. There would have been no trace that anybody was even there, except the rings were gone."
    det "El sistema de seguridad se reactivó. No habría quedado ningún rastro de que alguien hubiera estado allí, salvo que los anillos habían desaparecido."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:92
translate spanish jez3_a595c814:

    # pc "So he did it."
    pc "Así que fue él."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:93
translate spanish jez3_2cf2afa7:

    # det "It seems that way."
    det "Eso parece."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:94
translate spanish jez3_7b6c844b:

    # pc "Any clue where he got the meth?"
    pc "¿Alguna pista de dónde consiguió la metanfetamina?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:96
translate spanish jez3_6063143c:

    # det "God, there's no telling. That shit is all over Skyhill."
    det "Dios, ni idea. Esa mierda está por todo Skyhill."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:97
translate spanish jez3_399bdc0f:

    # pc "Really?"
    pc "¿En serio?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:99
translate spanish jez3_94032961:

    # det "Yes. That's what I've been working on. That's my primary job."
    det "Sí. En eso es en lo que he estado trabajando. Es mi trabajo principal."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:100
translate spanish jez3_91bebae5:

    # det "We know a few dealers and we can find people who buy meth."
    det "Conocemos a algunos traficantes y podemos encontrar gente que compra metanfetamina."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:101
translate spanish jez3_ec847758:

    # det "But we can't seem to locate where the shit is coming from. Somebody around here is cooking it, and I don't know where."
    det "Pero parece que no conseguimos localizar de dónde viene esa mierda. Alguien por aquí la está cocinando, y no sé dónde."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:102
translate spanish jez3_ea875425:

    # pc "I had no idea it was that bad around here."
    pc "No tenía ni idea de que la cosa estuviera tan mal por aquí."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:103
translate spanish jez3_49c82960:

    # det "Yeah. So I'm not sure exactly where your dad got it at, but I've been questioning people."
    det "Sí. Así que no estoy seguro de dónde la consiguió exactamente tu padre, pero he estado interrogando a gente."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:104
translate spanish jez3_5d188bd8:

    # det "Look [pcname], it sounds to me like your dad was having some sort of psychotic break."
    det "Mira [pcname], a mí me parece que tu padre estaba sufriendo algún tipo de crisis psicótica."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:105
translate spanish jez3_7a8cf8a1:

    # det "Teleporting hula-hoops, diamond theft, using meth to speed up your heart rate."
    det "Teleportar hula-hoops, robar diamantes, usar metanfetamina para acelerar el ritmo cardíaco."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:106
translate spanish jez3_8ebd5686:

    # det "That sounds like a bunch of nonsense to me."
    det "A mí me parece un montón de tonterías."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:107
translate spanish jez3_c417e350:

    # pc "Yeah."
    pc "Sí."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:108
translate spanish jez3_4c3ec6a3:

    # det "But the more we dig into it, the more likely we're going to find him."
    det "Pero cuanto más indaguemos, más posibilidades tendremos de encontrarlo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:109
translate spanish jez3_e004b1ab:

    # det "So keep digging."
    det "Así que sigue investigando."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:110
translate spanish jez3_58f0fc2d:

    # det "Send me the info that you found on the laptop and I'll see if I can find this Whitney person."
    det "Envíame la información que has encontrado en el portátil y veré si puedo localizar a esa tal Whitney."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:111
translate spanish jez3_955d194d:

    # det "Assuming that she's real and not somebody that your dad made up."
    det "Suponiendo que sea real y no alguien que se haya inventado tu padre."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:112
translate spanish jez3_25bfd7d2:

    # pc "It seems like she's real to me, based on the e-mails."
    pc "A mí me parece que es real, a juzgar por los correos electrónicos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:113
translate spanish jez3_2fc85b75:

    # det "Alright. Well let's find her."
    det "De acuerdo. Pues vamos a encontrarla."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:114
translate spanish jez3_e70c1658:

    # pc "I could e-mail her from Dad's laptop."
    pc "Podría enviarle un correo desde el portátil de papá."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:116
translate spanish jez3_3997e2c3:

    # det "That's not a bad idea. Give it a shot. Start up a conversation with her, see if you can find out more about her."
    det "No es mala idea. Inténtalo. Entabla una conversación con ella, a ver si puedes averiguar más sobre ella."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:117
translate spanish jez3_4d9bef33:

    # det "And let me know anything you find."
    det "Y cuéntame todo lo que descubras."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:119
translate spanish jez3_5bc44b07:

    # pc "I will."
    pc "Lo haré."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:121
translate spanish jez3_b734eba7:

    # det "Thanks for meeting me here. I needed this."
    det "Gracias por quedar conmigo aquí. Lo necesitaba."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:122
translate spanish jez3_ba520f30:

    # det "Now I have to get home. I haven't seen my kid in two days."
    det "Ahora tengo que irme a casa. Hace dos días que no veo a mi hijo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:123
translate spanish jez3_ce82357f:

    # pc "You have a kid?"
    pc "¿Tienes un hijo?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:125
translate spanish jez3_71fc0e0c:

    # det "Yeah, Javi. He's seven. My mom's taking care of him right now."
    det "Sí, Javi. Tiene siete años. Ahora mismo lo está cuidando mi madre."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:126
translate spanish jez3_798c23ff:

    # det "You surprised that I have a kid?"
    det "¿Te sorprende que tenga un hijo?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:130
translate spanish jez3_632e262d:

    # det "Thanks. I had him when I was 17."
    det "Gracias. Lo tuve cuando tenía 17 años."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:133
translate spanish jez3_ae370b70:

    # det "I'm not. You don't have to be married to have a kid, you know."
    det "No. No hace falta estar casada para tener un hijo, ya sabes."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:134
translate spanish jez3_2356fff3:

    # pc "Right, I didn't mean anything by it."
    pc "Claro, no quería decir nada con eso."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:137
translate spanish jez3_a82f6cf9:

    # det "Oh, I thought you seemed surprised."
    det "Oh, me pareció que te sorprendías."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:139
translate spanish jez3_12633b63:

    # det "Anyway, I better get home."
    det "En fin, mejor me voy a casa."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:140
translate spanish jez3_d0fa7dfb:

    # det "I'll see you later, [pcname]."
    det "Nos vemos luego, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:141
translate spanish jez3_7b4cad00:

    # pc "Bye Detective Rodriguez."
    pc "Adiós, detective Rodríguez."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:144
translate spanish jez3_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/jez_3_1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_3_1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:145
translate spanish jez3_e7adfac5:

    # det "You can call me Jez, okay? That's my first name."
    det "Puedes llamarme Jez, ¿vale? Es mi nombre de pila."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:146
translate spanish jez3_db79b546:

    # pc "Okay. Bye Jez."
    pc "Vale. Adiós, Jez."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:151
translate spanish jez3_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice 'voices/jez_goodnight.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_goodnight.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:152
translate spanish jez3_2f6a1cc2:

    # det "Good night."
    det "Buenas noches."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:155
translate spanish jez3_40a94195:

    # "She stands up and walks out of the bar. I sit there alone for a few minutes, thinking about our conversation."
    "Se levanta y sale del bar. Me quedo allí sentado solo unos minutos, pensando en nuestra conversación."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:156
translate spanish jez3_06361269:

    # "She thinks Dad was crazy. I'm not so sure."
    "Ella cree que papá estaba loco. Yo no estoy tan seguro."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:157
translate spanish jez3_d8c1ec54:

    # "The things in his notes and in his conversations with Whitney were wild, but there is so much there that seems true."
    "Las cosas que aparecen en sus notas y en sus conversaciones con Whitney eran descabelladas, pero hay mucho ahí que parece cierto."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:158
translate spanish jez3_3da12785:

    # "Whitney definitely seems like a real person. I just need to find out who she is."
    "Whitney parece, sin duda, una persona real. Solo tengo que averiguar quién es."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:159
translate spanish jez3_8298e18a:

    # "Then maybe I can find out where my dad went."
    "Entonces quizá pueda averiguar adónde se fue mi padre."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:160
translate spanish jez3_bc8a9774:

    # "Eventually, I stand up and walk out of the bar, then head home for the night."
    "Al final, me levanto y salgo del bar, y luego me dirijo a casa para pasar la noche."

translate spanish strings:

    # game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:2
    old "You need to get into your dad's computer. Talk to Adrian about it. She's been at the grocery store trying to find a new game."
    new "Tienes que acceder al ordenador de tu padre. Habla con Adrian sobre ello. Ella ha estado en la tienda de comestibles intentando encontrar un juego nuevo."

    # game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:3
    old "Once you search your dad's laptop, call Detective Rodriguez from your bedroom in the evening."
    new "Una vez que hayas registrado el portátil de tu padre, llama al detective Rodríguez desde tu habitación por la noche."

    # game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:35
    old "Sure, I'll be there in five minutes"
    new "Claro, estaré allí en cinco minutos."

    # game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:37
    old "That doesn't seem very professional"
    new "Eso no parece muy profesional."

    # game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:58
    old "Drink"
    new "Beber."

    # game/Scenes/Jez/jez3.rpy:61
